# Project Specific
# Since this script generates S4P files, we might want to exclude them if they are large
# However, usually we keep small example files.
# Let's exclude generated output files starting with timestamp (YYYYMMDD) or GMS_extracted
[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]_*.s4p
GMS_extracted_*.s4p

